    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept car in truly outstanding condition. It presents beautifully inside and out, with a very clean exterior, a well-preserved interior, and only the slightest signs of use consistent with a carefully maintained vehicle. This is the kind of car that stands out immediately for how fresh, complete, and properly cared-for it feels. A buyer can expect a top-tier example that needs nothing cosmetically and shows the level of ownership and upkeep you hope to find in a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 46900.0,
