      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking affordable transportation. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but offers solid value as an inexpensive daily driver, project car, or backup vehicle. Priced to sell and presented with straightforward appeal, this is a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels or a solid project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it has plenty of life and could be a great fit for the right buyer who appreciates a straightforward, no-nonsense vehicle. If you\u2019re after something cheap, usable, and full of potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with a strong mechanical foundation and plenty of upside. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed with good road manners. Not a show car, but a solid, honest platform for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a worthwhile weekend project. Recent attention to key service items helps it feel more sorted than most in this bracket. Priced to move for the buyer who recognizes a usable car with good bones.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Rough around the edges, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence you notice right away\u2014the lived-in charm, the unmistakable personality, the feeling that it still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal opportunity for someone who appreciates a vehicle with character, whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a practical spare, or a hands-on project with real potential. There\u2019s a rugged honesty here that makes it easy to imagine bringing it into your world and making it your own. A lot of life remains in this one for the right buyer who sees more than just transportation\u2014they see possibility.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity with straightforward value, this vehicle is best suited for buyers seeking simple, affordable transportation. It shows its age cosmetically, but offers a practical path into ownership at an accessible price point. An honest, no-nonsense option for someone who values utility and low upfront cost.",
      "price": 5950.0,
